descriptionHtml:
When you accidentally delete important images, photos or videos from the SD card or internal memory, do you feel a headache?
Now, you only need to download this application and make it scan all the internal and external memory of your phone to find what you want to recover. Never worry about losing data again!

No need root , no matter you accidentally deleted photos or reformatted the SD card, this application can use deep media digdeep algorithm and powerful data recovery function to find and recover lost pictures, videos and other files.

How it works
It's very simple, after downloading this application first, just start the application. The file classification page is displayed. Please select the file type you need to recover and then enter this page. After entering this page, the loading progress will be displayed, please wait patiently until it scans the deleted photos in all folders and files. It may take a while, depending on your memory size. After the search is complete, it will arrange your photos one by one in order of date. Please select the images you need to recover and click the "Recover" button to restore them. After recovery, it will tell you in which folder the recovered image was found.

We also provide one-to-one service from data experts to provide more advanced solutions to your file recovery problems.

* Restore all video types: mp4, 3gp, avi, mov.
* One-to-one data expert service, providing the best quality processing methods.
* Supports 30 languages ​​and can perform media discovery without connecting to the Internet.
